name: OLLIE WOLF
description:
The ollie is the foundation to almost every trick in skateboarding. Look down at the skateboard - keep your weight evenly balanced over both legs. Jump as you would if you didn't have a board under your feet, and let it free! 

The Wolf!  is a resident of Skatopia with ollie as his favorite trick, flies full of passion and fun. His mission is to spread ollie to all corners of the galaxy so that everyone knows the basics of skateboarding.
